### ============================================
### Flight Search
### ============================================
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/flights/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "origin": "CGK",
    "destination": "DPS",
    "departure_date": "2025-12-15",
    "return_date": "2025-12-20",
    "passengers": 1,
    "cabin_class": "economy"
}

